RESEARCH ALERT - Hitachi Zosen cut . Yamaichi Research Institute of Securities and Economics Inc said it downgraded Hitachi Zosen Corp to a " 2 " rating from its previous " 1 " . In its three - grade rating system , the research institute assigns a " 2 " rating to issues whose values it sees moving within 10 percentage points in either direction of the Tokyo Stock Exchange first - section TOPIX index over the next six months . 
